data.description: Elegantly designed, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom cottage boasts luxurious touches throughout. Step into a world of sophistication with high-end finishes that adorn every corner. The deluxe kitchen features exquisite stone countertops paired with top-of-the-line appliances, including a wine fridge and ice maker, catering to culinary enthusiasts. A gas fireplace creates a cozy ambiance in the living room while you immerse yourself in the surround sound experience. The primary bedroom and bath are true retreats, offering ample space, a generously sized bathtub, a walk-in shower, and a sense of tranquility. The custom walk-in closet provides practicality and style, ensuring your belongings are impeccably organized. Outside, a covered rear porch and generously sized fenced yard set the stage for relaxation and play. Nestled in a prime location, this residence is conveniently situated mere blocks away from shopping, dining, and the charming downtown area of Old Gretna, effortlessly combining comfort, style, and convenience.
